## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the complexity of human trafficking, which varies significantly across different regions and contexts. Additionally, the effectiveness of proposed solutions may differ based on local legal, social, and economic conditions. Further research and collaboration with local anti-trafficking organizations are recommended to tailor strategies effectively.